summary: This mod adds a fully functional Ash Spawn follower named \"Ash Ketchup\" in Riverwood. You need the Dragonborn DLC for this mod to work properly.
descriptionHtml:
This mod adds a fully functional Ash Spawn follower named \"Ash Ketchup\"  in Riverwood. You need the Dragonborn DLC for this mod to work properly.

These pictures were taken with my ENB, found here: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/40456//?]Subtle ENB by Bill[/url]

Check out my other mods: [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/users/4831711/?tb=mods&pUp=1]My Mods[/url]

Thanks for your time, and enjoy the mod!
author: billmineface
